snippet.title: Vortex Point 6 - Walkthrough
snippet.description:
0:23 - get wallet
0:25 - get finger print kit
0:33 - get smartphone
1:38 - use finger print kit #1
2:41 - get free carnival admission  coupon
2:50 - use smartphone
3:05 - get cotton candy coupon
3:21 - get gum
3:25 - get cotton candy
3:36 - get bolt cutter

3:54 - give finger prints to Caroline
4:42 - give cotton candy to Craig, get stick
4:57 - attach stick to gum
5:01 - use stick on gum
5:44 - use screw
6:05 - get Ghost Train coupon
6:17 - use bolt cutter
6:33 - use haunted chain, get riddle
7:04 - get statue
8:16 - hit button

Alternative 2nd ending: https://youtu.be/S-vx0HCg20I
